name: Backed Swiss Domestic Government Bond 0-3
description: Backed Swiss Domestic Government Bond 0-3 (bCSBGC3) is a tracker certificate issued as an ERC-20 token. bCSBGC3 tracks the price of iShares Swiss Domestic Government Bond 0-3 ETF. bCSBGC3 is designed to give eligible cryptocurrency market participants regulatory-compliant access to the stock price of iShares Swiss Domestic Government Bond 0-3 ETF.
